'''傑森·康尼''' {{post-nominals|country=CAN|MLA|PC}}（{{lang|en|Jason Kenney}}，{{bd|1968年|5月30日||}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，現任[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]][[亞伯達省省長|省長]]、亞省[[聯合保守黨|聯合保守黨]]黨魁和[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]卡加利-羅歇選區省議員。他於2017年當選末任亞伯達進步保守黨黨魁，同年促成該黨與亞省另一右翼政黨野玫瑰黨合併為聯合保守黨，2019年帶領該黨贏取省選後出任省長。在此之前他曾活躍於加拿大聯邦政壇，1997年至2016年間先後以[[加拿大改革黨|加拿大改革黨]]、[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]和[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]黨員身份出任[[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]][[加拿大國會下議院|下議院]]議員，並曾於保守黨執政期間擔任[[加拿大內閣|聯邦內閣]]成員，先後出任[[加拿大公民及移民部|公民及移民部长]]、[[加拿大就业及社会发展部|就业及社会发展部长]]和[[加拿大国防部|国防部长]]。

==早年生活==
康尼於[[安大略省|安大略省]][[奧克維爾_(安大略省)|奧克維爾]]出生<ref name="Herald170318">{{cite news|first=James|last=Wood|url=http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/profile-of-jason-kenney|title=From 'Snack Pack' to leader of the Progressive Conservatives: How Jason Kenney got to where he is now|work=The Calgary Herald|date=2017-03-18|accessdate=2017-08-10|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208160945/https://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/profile-of-jason-kenney|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父親羅拔為戰機機師和教師<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/leaderpost/obituary.aspx?n=martin-kenney&pid=141783748|title=Martin Kenney's Obituary on Leader-Post|publisher=|access-date=2017-08-10|archive-date=2017-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619212338/http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/leaderpost/obituary.aspx?n=martin-kenney&pid=141783748|dead-url=no}}</ref>，祖父則為爵士音樂家馬特·康尼（{{lang|en|Mart Kenney}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/HousePublications/Publication.aspx?DocId=2332780&Language=E&Mode=1&Parl=36&Ses=1#LINK87|title=MART KENNEY|date=1998-03-17|author=Hansard, House of Commons, Canada, 36th Parliament, 1st Session|access-date=2017-08-10|archive-date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108044747/http://www.parl.gc.ca/HousePublications/Publication.aspx?DocId=2332780&Language=E&Mode=1&Parl=36&Ses=1#LINK87|dead-url=no}}</ref>。康尼年幼時一家先遷至[[緬尼托巴省|緬尼托巴省]][[溫尼伯|溫尼伯]]，後再遷居[[薩斯喀徹溫省|薩斯喀徹溫省]]小鎮威爾科克斯（{{lang|en|Wilcox}}）<ref name="Herald170318"/>。

康尼中學畢業後到由[[耶穌會|耶穌會]]營運的私立[[舊金山大學|舊金山大學]]修讀哲學，並改信天主教<ref name="Herald170318"/>。他在該校期間活躍於學生會活動，並曾嘗試阻止支持墮胎組織在該校校園活動<ref name="Herald170318"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=yhlC-ZrguhA|title=Jason Kenney interviewed by CNN, undated, between 1986-1988|access-date=2017-08-10|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120013903/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yhlC-ZrguhA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他其後終止大學學業並加入薩斯喀徹溫自由黨<ref>{{cite web|first=Douglas|last=Todd|url=http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2010/12/31/jason-kenney-versus-his-own-catholic-church/|title=Jason Kenney versus his own Catholic church|work=The Vancouver Sun|date=December 31, 2010|accessdate=2015-05-26|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526095225/http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2010/12/31/jason-kenney-versus-his-own-catholic-church/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1988年成為該黨黨魁葛代爾（{{lang|en|Ralph Goodale}}）的行政助理<ref name="KeungBlack">{{cite news|last1=Keung|first1=Nicholas|last2=Black|first2=Debra|title=Q & A: Jason Kenney on his role as Canada's immigration minister|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/immigration/2013/02/22/q_a_jason_kenney_on_his_role_as_canadas_immigration_minister.html|accessdate=20 July 2016|work=The Toronto Star|date=22 February 2013|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225221306/https://www.thestar.com/news/immigration/2013/02/22/q_a_jason_kenney_on_his_role_as_canadas_immigration_minister.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，他逐漸意識到自己的政治取態偏向保守<ref name="KeungBlack"/>，因此離開該黨並於1989年成為亞伯達納税人協會的首任行政總監，期間不時要求該省的執政進步保守黨政府削減開支<ref name="Herald170318"/>。他其後轉任加拿大納税人聯會主席<ref name="Herald170318"/>。

==晉身國會==
[[File:Jason_Kenney_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]

康尼任職納税人協會期間的表現獲[[加拿大改革黨|加拿大改革黨]]黨魁曼寧（{{lang|en|Preston Manning}}）賞識，曼寧因此羅致他於1997年聯邦大選中代表該黨出戰[[卡加利|卡加利]]東南選區<ref name="Herald170318"/>。康尼順利在該選區當選國會議員，首度晉身國會下議院。改革黨為該屆下議院的[[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]，而康尼亦獲任命為[[影子內閣|影子內閣]]稅務評議員<ref name="Herald170318"/><ref name="PARLINFO">{{cite web |url=https://lop.parl.ca/ParlInfo/Files/Parliamentarian.aspx?Item=106c623c-3606-40ae-a2f6-f4a619cf02f6&Language=E&Section=ALL |title=KENNEY, The Hon. Jason, P.C. |publisher=[[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]] |accessdate=2017-08-10 |archive-date=2017-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811110613/https://lop.parl.ca/ParlInfo/Files/Parliamentarian.aspx?Item=106c623c-3606-40ae-a2f6-f4a619cf02f6&Language=E&Section=ALL |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當時加拿大聯邦層面的右翼票源由改革黨和[[加拿大進步保守黨|進步保守黨]]攤分，兩黨未能挑戰[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]的執政地位。曼寧因此在改革黨内成立聯合替代委員會（{{lang|en|United Alternative}}），以求結合該兩聯邦右翼政黨，並委任康尼為該委員會成員之一<ref name="Herald170318"/>。

改革黨於2000年改組成[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]後，康尼支持[[戴國衛|戴國衛]]競逐該黨黨魁<ref name="Herald170318"/>；戴國衞最終壓倒曼寧當選黨魁。在同年11月舉行的聯邦大選中，康尼代表加拿大聯盟在卡加利東南選區連任國會議員。加拿大聯盟成為該屆下議院的官方反對黨，康尼則獲任為影子內閣財政評議員<ref name="PARLINFO"/>。他於2002年12月調任美國事務評議員<ref name="PARLINFO"/>，期間支持美國於2003年對[[伊拉克戰爭|伊拉克開戰]]，並批評時任自由黨政府反對攻打伊拉克的立場有損[[美加關係|美加關係]]<ref>Maria Babbage, "Liberal stance will make it tougher to avoid new border measures, says Alliance", ''Canadian Press NewsWire'', March 27, 2003.</ref>。

加拿大聯盟和進步保守黨於2003年末合併成新的[[加拿大保守黨|聯邦保守黨]]，而康尼則於[[2004年加拿大聯邦大選|2004年聯邦大選]]中代表保守黨保著卡加利東南選區議席，並於同年10月獲任為下議院反對黨副領袖<ref name="PARLINFO"/>。

2005年1月，时任总理[[保罗·马丁|保罗·马丁]]访华，康尼陪同。期间，康尼自行前往刚逝世的[[赵紫阳|赵紫阳]]家中吊唁，成为第一位，也是至2022年时唯一一位访问赵紫阳住所的外国政要<ref name="cbc">{{cite web|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/5-1-22/25933.html|title=Canada Expresses Condolences Over Zhao Ziyang's Death|publisher=The Epoch Times|date=2005-01-22|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050421175343/http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/5-1-22/25933.html|archivedate=2005-04-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/5-1-22/25933.html|title=Canada Expresses Condolences Over Zhao Ziyang's Death|publisher=The Epoch Times|date=2005-01-22|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050421175343/http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/5-1-22/25933.html|archivedate=2005-04-21}}</ref>。康尼在赵的住处外先是受中国政府当局人员的阻挠，后在一位自称赵紫阳生前助理的带领下到达赵的住处，并在翻译的帮助下留下了中文的吊言<ref name="cbc" />。事后接受采访时，他希望能有更多的外国人向在中国的地下民主运动表达他们象征性的支持<ref name="cbc" />。马丁回应康尼径自访问不尊重家属意愿，同时也说自己没能到访有“其他原因”<ref name="cbc" />；康尼一周后在国会质询时反呛马丁所称不符事实，在提到[[六四事件|天安门屠杀]]及其中赵的作用的同时批评马丁政府访华时从未向中国方面提及人权议题。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ourcommons.ca/DocumentViewer/en/38-1/house/sitting-46/hansard#Int-1092959|date=2005-01-31|title=38TH PARLIAMENT, 1ST SESSION, EDITED HANSARD, NUMBER 046|language=en|publisher=[[加拿大下议院|House of Commons]]}}</ref>。

==聯邦內閣==
===國會秘書及國務部長===

保守黨於2006年聯邦大選壓倒自由黨贏取少數政府，連任國會議員的康尼則獲任為新任[[加拿大總理|總理]][[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]的多元文化事務國會秘書<ref name="Herald170318"/>，再於2007年調任多元文化事務及加拿大身份國務部長<ref name="PARLINFO"/>，期間他負責處理哈珀政府與少數族裔國民之間的關係，並走訪國內多個少數族裔社區<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.thestar.com/News/Canada/article/306284bn=1|title = Travelling Tory woos ethnic voters.|publisher = ''Toronto Star''|accessdate = 2009-12-04|date = 2008-02-23|archive-date = 2012-10-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020115439/http://www.thestar.com/News/Canada/article/306284bn=1|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他於2008年5月開展社區歷史認知計劃（{{lang|en|Community Historical Recognition Program}}），五年之間向國內數個少數族裔社群的機構撥出總共1350萬元經費，以宣揚相關族裔在加國的歷史。受惠的少數族裔社群多在過去受加拿大主流社會歧視，當中包括[[意大利裔加拿大人|意大利裔]]、[[華裔加拿大人|華裔]]、印裔和猶太人<ref name=":2">{{cite web|url=http://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/welcome-to-my-world/|title=The inside story of Jason Kenney's campaign to win over ethnic votes|last=Castonguay|first=Alec|date=February 2, 2013|website=|publisher=Maclean's|language=en-US|access-date=July 9, 2016|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501213604/https://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/welcome-to-my-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===公民及移民部長===
康尼於[[2008年加拿大聯邦大選|2008年聯邦大選]]連任國會議員，後獲調任為[[加拿大公民及移民部|聯邦公民、移民及多元文化部長]]<ref name="PARLINFO"/>，正式晉身內閣。他在任期間執政保守黨政府修改了《加拿大國籍法》，影響在加拿大國外誕下子女的加國公民。新例下在外國出生的兒童，必須有其中一名家長在加拿大境內誕生才可獲加拿大公民身份。此外，其他國家駐在加拿大的外交或政府人員若在加拿大誕下子女的話，其中一名家長須為加拿大公民或永久居民，那些子女才可獲加拿大公民身份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/citizenship/rules.asp#understand |title=Changes to citizenship rules as of April 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420015439/http://www.cic.gc.ca/ENGLISH/citizenship/rules.asp#understand |archivedate=2009年4月20日 |df= |access-date=2017年8月11日 }}</ref>。

加拿大新聞社報道指康尼阻止聯邦政府在2010年印製的新版入籍試參考指南中提及有關[[加拿大同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的資訊<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/article/773841--kenney-blocked-gay-rights-in-citizenship-guide-documents?bn=1 | title=Kenney blocked gay rights in citizenship guide: documents | date=2010-03-02 | work=The Star | first=Dean | last=Beeby | accessdate=October 4, 2015 | archive-date=2012-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020115030/http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/article/773841--kenney-blocked-gay-rights-in-citizenship-guide-documents?bn=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>；2011年版入籍試指南則有一句提及相關資訊<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/citizenship-guide-gets-single-sentence-on-gay-rights-1.618396 |title=Citizenship guide gets single sentence on gay rights |date=March 14, 2011 |publisher=CTV News |accessdate=2017-08-11 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610130734/https://www.ctvnews.ca/citizenship-guide-gets-single-sentence-on-gay-rights-1.618396 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

康尼於2010年3月宣布改革加拿大難民制度，當中承諾收納多2500名在聯合國難民營和都市貧民窟棲身的難民，令名額增至14500人<ref name="jasonkenney1">{{cite web|url=http://www.jasonkenney.com/EN/4961/109603|title=Expanding Canada's Refugee Resettlement Programs|date=2010-04-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100510073044/http://www.jasonkenney.com/EN/4961/109603|archivedate=2010-05-10|access-date=2017-08-11}}</ref>。他亦承諾在2011-12年度收取的難民總數將較往年為多，但最終該年度所收取的難民數目卻下跌26%至30年新低，被國內難民組織批評<ref>{{Cite news|work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|title=Canada Witnesses Dramatic Drop In Resettled Refugees Despite Pledge to Grant More Asylum|date=March 8, 2013|url=http://ca.ibtimes.com/articles/443807/20130308/canada-refugee-council.htm|accessdate=November 14, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420030024/http://ca.ibtimes.com/articles/443807/20130308/canada-refugee-council.htm|archivedate=2013-04-20}}</ref>。

保守黨於[[2011年加拿大聯邦大選|2011年聯邦大選]]首次贏取多數政府，評論將部分功勞歸予康尼，指他與少數族裔社群建立的基礎為保守黨開拓新票源<ref name="Herald170318"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/how-courting-the-immigrant-vote-paid-off-for-the-tories/article578608/ |title=How courting the immigrant vote paid off for the Tories |publisher=theglobeandmail.com |date=2011-05-03 |accessdate=2013-03-23 |location=Toronto |archive-date=2020-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225015029/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/how-courting-the-immigrant-vote-paid-off-for-the-tories/article578608/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。連任議員的康尼留任公民及移民部長，並兌現保守黨的其中一項競選承諾，成功爭取在外交部之下新設宗教自由辦公室，確保加國人民在國內免受宗教壓迫，並向別國推廣宗教自由<ref name="Ottawa Citizen">{{cite web |last1=Berthiaume |first1=Lee |url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/faith-groups-call-on-liberals-to-keep-office-of-religious-freedom |title=Faith groups call on Liberals to keep Office of Religious Freedom |date=January 22, 2016 |accessdate=July 3, 2016 |publisher=Ottawa Citizen |archive-date=2019-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190623161532/https://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/faith-groups-call-on-liberals-to-keep-office-of-religious-freedom |dead-url=no }}</ref>；該辦公室於2016年被新任自由黨政府關閉<ref>{{cite web|last1=Evan|first1=Solomon|title=In defense of the office of religious freedom|url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/in-defence-of-the-defunct-office-of-religious-freedom/|website=macleans.ca|publisher=Maclean's Magazine|accessdate=July 5, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113322/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/in-defence-of-the-defunct-office-of-religious-freedom/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年7月，康尼宣布聯邦政府有意褫奪1800名透過欺詐途徑入籍的加拿大公民資格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/07/20/pol-kenney-immigration-visas.html|title=Ottawa targets 1,800 in citizenship crackdown|work=CBC News|date=July 20, 2011|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2012-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110001232/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/07/20/pol-kenney-immigration-visas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於同年12月宣布即時禁止出席入籍儀式的準公民在宣誓入籍時佩戴[[尼卡布|尼卡布]]等覆蓋面部的服飾<ref name="CBC111212">{{cite web |first1=Laura |last1=Payton |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/face-veils-banned-for-citizenship-oaths-1.1048750 |title=Face veils banned for citizenship oaths |date=2011-12-12 |accessdate=2017-08-10 |publisher=CBC News |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510181027/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/face-veils-banned-for-citizenship-oaths-1.1048750 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；加拿大聯邦法院於2015年2月裁定該項規定違法，聯邦上訴庭則於同年10月維持原判<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/10/05/niqab-ban-citizenship-cer_n_8247678.html|title=Zunera Ishaq, Niqab-Wearing Woman, Can Take Citizenship Oath Says Judge|work=Huffington Post|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2017-08-10|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811104333/http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/10/05/niqab-ban-citizenship-cer_n_8247678.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===就業及社會發展部長===
總理哈珀於2013年7月重組內閣，康尼調任為[[加拿大就业及社会发展部|就業及社會發展部長]]<ref name="PARLINFO"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2013-07-16/headline1373963562d4597843.html|title=新設就業和社會發展部長 首要改善就業 哈珀連任重注押康尼|work=《星島日報》加東版|date=2013-07-16|accessdate=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607015042/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2013-07-16/headline1373963562d4597843.html|archive-date=2017-06-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。就加拿大退休金計劃（{{lang|en|Canada Pension Plan}}）和老年保障金（{{lang|en|Old Age Security}}）有大量申請人的殘疾狀況被拒後申訴重審程序過於緩慢，他於2014年11月承諾加快審核該些積壓個案<ref>{{cite web |first1=Lee-Anne |last1=Goodman |work=Canadian Press |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/11/27/large_social_security_backlog_unacceptable_kenney_says.html |title=Large social security backlog unacceptable, Kenney says |date=2011-12-12 |accessdate=2017-08-10 |publisher=The Toronto Star |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804153117/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/11/27/large_social_security_backlog_unacceptable_kenney_says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國防部長===
[[File:U.S._Secretary_of_Defense_Ash_Carter_meets_Canadian_Minister_of_National_Defense_Jason_Kenney_at_NATO_Headquarters_in_Brussels,_Belgium.jpg|thumb]]總部與美國國防部長[[阿什頓·卡特|阿什頓·卡特]]會面]]

康尼於2015年2月調任為[[加拿大國防部|加拿大國防部]]部长，同時兼任多元文化部長<ref name="PARLINFO"/><ref name="Cabinet shuffle">{{cite web | url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2015/02/09/conservative-cabinet-shuffle-makes-jason-kenney-defence-minister.html | title=Jason Kenney new defence minister in Conservative cabinet shuffle | publisher=''Toronto Star'' | date=February 9, 2015 | accessdate=September 17, 2015 | author=Boutilier, Alex | archive-date=2021-03-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311153152/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2015/02/09/conservative-cabinet-shuffle-makes-jason-kenney-defence-minister.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-02-10/canada1423565849d5434419.html|title=倪可森接任外長 康尼兼任防長|work=《星島日報》卡加利版|date=2015-02-10|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811223259/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-02-10/canada1423565849d5434419.html|archive-date=2017-08-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他任防長期間對國家安全採強硬立場，表示加國須打擊[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]武裝分子以防他們對加國構成威脅<ref name="India born former soldier sworn in as Canada's new defense minister">{{cite web|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idCAKCN0ST2LV20151104|title=India-born former soldier sworn in as Canada's new defense minister|last=Schnurr|first=Leah|date=November 4, 2015|website=Reuters.ca|publisher=Reuters|access-date=July 7, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142145/https://ca.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idCAKCN0ST2LV20151104|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年3月中，康尼表示[[皇家加拿大海軍|皇家加拿大海軍]]船艦在[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]對出海域參與[[北約|北約]]任務時受到俄羅斯軍艦對抗，而俄羅斯戰機更於低空以高速掠過加軍的弗雷德里克頓號戰艦<ref name="NATO Kenney">{{cite web | url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/canadian-politics/dnd-russian-confrontation-claims | title=NATO officials contradict Jason Kenney's claim that Russian fighter jets flew over Canadian navy frigate | publisher=National Post | date=March 14, 2015 | accessdate=September 17, 2015 | author=Pugliese, David}}</ref>。然而，北約官員其後表示俄方軍艦從遠處可見但沒有靠近北約艦隊，而俄方戰機亦一直於高空飛行<ref name="NATO Kenney" />。

同年3月末，康尼表示加軍對抗伊斯蘭國的空襲有必要伸延至敘利亞境內，因為盟國空軍中只有美軍和加軍的戰機有能力使用[[精確導引武器|精確導引武器]]。然而，實際上沙特阿拉伯和阿聯酋軍方亦曾使用那些武器，並獲美國陸軍上將[[馬丁·登普西|登普西]]認可<ref name="Lawson crater">{{cite web | url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/defence-watch/gen-tom-lawson-tries-to-dig-jason-kenney-out-of-a-bomb-crater-of-his-own-making | title=Gen. Tom Lawson tries to dig Jason Kenney out of a bomb crater of his own making | publisher=Ottawa Citizen | date=March 30, 2015 | accessdate=September 17, 2015 | author=Pugliese, David | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100845/http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/defence-watch/gen-tom-lawson-tries-to-dig-jason-kenney-out-of-a-bomb-crater-of-his-own-making | dead-url=no }}</ref>。時任加拿大國防參謀長羅森將軍（{{lang|en|Tom Lawson}}）發表聲明為康尼的言論辯護，但其後卻撤回聲明並為該聲明的内容有誤致歉<ref name="About face">{{cite web | url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/canadian-politics/about-face-as-canadas-top-general-admits-letter-backing-jason-kenney-on-smart-missiles-is-incorrect | title=About-face as Canada's top general admits letter backing Jason Kenney on smart missiles is incorrect | publisher=National Post | date=April 1, 2015 | accessdate=September 17, 2015 | author=Pugliese, David}}</ref>。國防部内消息人士指康尼的下屬曾向羅森施壓，要求他發表該份聲明<ref name="About face" />。

同年4月，康尼宣布派遣加軍到烏克蘭，在當地訓練烏克蘭軍隊的軍人。加軍於同年9月抵達鄰近烏克蘭和波蘭邊境的[[亞沃里夫|亞沃里夫]]，駐在當地的烏克蘭軍隊國際安全及維和中心<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2015/09/01/canadian-soldiers-land-in-ukraine-for-training-mission|title=Canadian soldiers land in Ukraine for training mission|last=Warmington|first=Joe|date=September 1, 2015|website=Toronto Sun|publisher=Toronto Sun|access-date=July 8, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129232216/https://torontosun.com/2015/09/01/canadian-soldiers-land-in-ukraine-for-training-mission|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==轉戰省政==
卡加利東南選區在[[2015年加拿大聯邦大選|2015年聯邦大選]]舉行前解散，康尼改到新成立的卡加利密拿坡選區（{{lang|en|Calgary Midnapore}}）參選並成功連任國會議員。然而，保守黨在該屆大選失利，自由黨以多數政府姿態重拾執政權，哈珀因此辭去保守黨黨魁職務。康尼被外界視為繼任黨魁的熱門人選<ref name="ch">{{cite news|title=Election results promise repercussions for all party leaders|url=http://thechronicleherald.ca/opinion/1317345-howe-room-election-results-promise-repercussions-for-all-party-leaders|accessdate=October 19, 2015|work=Chronicle-Herald|date=October 18, 2015|archive-date=2018-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180909112853/http://thechronicleherald.ca/opinion/1317345-howe-room-election-results-promise-repercussions-for-all-party-leaders|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="who">{{cite news|title=Who will replace Steven Harper as leader of the Conservatives?|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/canadian-politics/who-will-replace-steven-harper-as-leader-of-the-progressive-conservatives|accessdate=October 20, 2015|work=National Post|date=October 20, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/277910/2015-10-22/post-9%E7%B9%BC%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88/?variant=zh-hk|title=9繼任人選名單康尼領先|work=《星島日報》加西版|date=2015-10-22|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812021329/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/277910/2015-10-22/post-9%E7%B9%BC%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他於2016年6月透露正在考慮轉戰亞省政壇<ref>{{cite news|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/958965/2016-06-23/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%EF%B8%B0%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%BF%94%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E5%BE%9E%E6%94%BF/?variant=zh-hk|title=康尼︰正考慮返亞省從政|work=《星島日報》加東版|date=2016-06-23|accessdate=2017-08-11}}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，並於同年7月正式宣布參選亞伯達進步保守黨黨魁，以填補[[彭迪思|彭迪思]]辭職後所遺下的空缺<ref>{{cite news|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/1012384/2016-07-15/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%AF%E8%B4%8F%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%86%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/?variant=zh-hk|title=康尼選亞省保守黨領 民意指可贏下屆省選|work=《星島日報》加東版|date=2016-07-15|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812021805/http://toronto.singtao.ca/1012384/2016-07-15/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%AF%E8%B4%8F%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%86%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2017-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他的主要目標為結合亞省兩大右翼政黨進步保守黨和野玫瑰黨，以求團結右派票源在下屆省選擊敗尋求連任的左翼亞伯達新民主黨<ref name="Herald160706">{{cite web|last1=James|first1=Wood|url=http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/kenney-to-announce-run-for-pc-leadership-on-wednesday|title=Kenney finally makes his leadership pitch to 'Unite Alberta'|date=July 6, 2016|website=calgaryherald.com|publisher=Calgary Herald|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510121149/http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/kenney-to-announce-run-for-pc-leadership-on-wednesday|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於同年9月辭去卡加利密拿坡選區國會議員職務<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/jason-kenney-to-resign-federal-seat-next-week-1.3760314|title=Kenney resigning as MP after 19 years in bid to 'unite the right' in Alberta|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113537/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/jason-kenney-to-resign-federal-seat-next-week-1.3760314|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=resign>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jason-kenney-canadian-taxpayers-federation-alberta-1.3668514|title=Taxpayers group miffed Kenney will collect MP perks this summer|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308042651/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jason-kenney-canadian-taxpayers-federation-alberta-1.3668514|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/774753/2016-09-23/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E7%B1%B2%E3%80%8C%E6%B1%82%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%98%E7%95%B0%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk|title=康尼離任國會議員 籲「求同存異」|work=《星島日報》加西版|date=2016-09-23|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812055653/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/774753/2016-09-23/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E7%B1%B2%E3%80%8C%E6%B1%82%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%98%E7%95%B0%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2017年3月舉行的亞伯達進步保守黨黨魁選舉中，康尼在首輪投票以壓倒性的75%得票率當選黨魁<ref>{{cite news|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/1612787/2017-03-19/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%9675%E5%A3%93%E5%80%92%E6%80%A7%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8-%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%BB%A8%E9%AD%81/?variant=zh-hk|title=康尼取75%壓倒性選票 當選亞省保守黨黨魁|work=《星島日報》加東版|date=2017-03-19|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812021503/http://toronto.singtao.ca/1612787/2017-03-19/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%9675%E5%A3%93%E5%80%92%E6%80%A7%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8-%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%BB%A8%E9%AD%81/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2017-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。進步保守黨和野玫瑰黨在往後數星期就合併事宜磋商，於同年5月中公布達成兩黨合併的臨時協議<ref>{{cite news|url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1157348/2017-05-19/post-%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%812%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%87%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%AC%B2%E7%95%B6%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/?variant=zh-hk|title=亞省2右翼政黨將合併 康尼欲當黨領角逐省選|work=《星島日報》加西版|date=2017-05-19|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812055837/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1157348/2017-05-19/post-%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%812%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%87%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E6%AC%B2%E7%95%B6%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E7%9C%81%E9%81%B8/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2017-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Graney|first1=Emma|title=Wildrose-PC members to vote on new united party on July 22|url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/politics/alberta-conservative-unity-one-step-closer|accessdate=2017-08-11|work=Edmonton Journal|date=2017-05-18|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730015835/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/politics/alberta-conservative-unity-one-step-closer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩黨黨員於同年7月22日投票通過合併<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/wildrose-unity-pcs-vote-1.4217598|title=Wildrose and PC members approve unite-the-right deal with 95% voting Yes|publisher=CBC News|first=Michelle|last=Bellefontaine|date=2017-07-22|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811055312/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/wildrose-unity-pcs-vote-1.4217598|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兩黨遂告解散並由新成立的[[聯合保守黨|聯合保守黨]]取代；康尼則於同年7月29日宣布角逐聯合保守黨黨魁職務<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/jason-kenney-leadership-announcement-1.4227737|title=Jason Kenney launches UCP leadership campaign with criticism of PM, Alberta NDP|publisher=CBC News|first=Kyle|last=Muzyka|date=2017-07-29|accessdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034346/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/jason-kenney-leadership-announcement-1.4227737|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黨魁選舉結果於同年10月28日公布，康尼在首輪投票以61.1%得票率當選聯合保守黨首任黨魁<ref name="星島171031">{{cite news|url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1431712/2017-10-31/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98/?variant=zh-hk|title=康尼當選亞省聯合保守黨領|work=《星島日報》加西版|date=2017-10-31|accessdate=2017-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107011438/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/1431712/2017-10-31/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2017-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/united-conservative-party-announce-new-leader-1.4377206|title=Jason Kenney elected 1st leader of Alberta's United Conservative Party|publisher=CBC News|first=Michelle|last=Bellefontaine|date=2017-10-28|accessdate=2017-11-02|archive-date=2017-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171101224123/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/united-conservative-party-announce-new-leader-1.4377206|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月1日，羅德尼（{{lang|en|Dave Rodney}}）辭去卡加利-羅歇選區（{{lang|en|Calgary-Lougheed}}）省議員職務，讓康尼參與該選區補選從而晉身[[亞伯達省議會|省議會]]<ref name="星島171031"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jason-kenney-gets-to-work-new-leader-upc-1.4377594|title=Calgary MLA steps down to allow Jason Kenney to run for legislature seat|publisher=CBC News|first=Michelle|last=Bellefontaine|date=2017-10-29|accessdate=2017-11-02|archive-date=2018-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803191702/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jason-kenney-gets-to-work-new-leader-upc-1.4377594|dead-url=no}}</ref>。康尼於同年12月14日舉行的補選中順利當選該選區省議員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/calgary-lougheed-byelection-advance-polls-open-voting-1.4446604|title=Kenney gains seat to tackle Notley head to head in legislature after resounding byelection victory|publisher=CBC News|first=Carly|last=Stagg|date=2017-12-15|accessdate=2018-01-24|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208134503/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/calgary-lougheed-byelection-advance-polls-open-voting-1.4446604|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並隨之出任亞伯達官方反對黨主席。

在2019年4月舉行的省選中，聯合保守黨贏取省議會87席中的63席，以多數姿態上台執政，康尼則於同月30日宣誓就任省長<ref>{{cite news|title=康尼宣誓任亞省省長 暫不斷卑詩油氣供應|url=https://www.singtao.ca/3416428/2019-05-01/post-%E5%BA%B7%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E7%9C%81%E9%95%B7-%E6%9A%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E6%B2%B9%E6%B0%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2019-05-04|newspaper=《星島日報》|date=2019-05-01|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504223145/https://www.singtao.ca/3416428/2019-05-01/post-%e5%ba%b7%e5%b0%bc%e5%ae%a3%e8%aa%93%e4%bb%bb%e4%ba%9e%e7%9c%81%e7%9c%81%e9%95%b7-%e6%9a%ab%e4%b8%8d%e6%96%b7%e5%8d%91%e8%a9%a9%e6%b2%b9%e6%b0%a3%e4%be%9b%e6%87%89/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

康尼在2022年5月18日的聯合保守黨黨魁審查投票中以51.4%的微弱多數通過了審查，儘管如此，康尼還是選擇宣布辭去亞伯塔省省長和聯合保守黨黨魁職務<ref>{{cite news|title=省長康尼宣布辭職|url=https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/22/5/19/n13740960.htm|accessdate=2022-05-19|newspaper=《卡爾加里大紀元》|date=2022-05-19|archive-date=2022-05-19}}</ref>。

